Admin Commands
Command	Description
/setfee <percent>	            Set escrow fee percentage
/ban <user_id> <reason>         Ban a user from using escrow services
/unban <user_id> <reason>       Unban a user
/broadcast <message>            Send a message to all users
/refund <trade_id> <reason>     Refund escrow funds

